descriptionHtml:
New huge hardcore dungeon full of interesting secrets, traps, treasures, secret ways and other interesting things. It\'s NOT a boring dungeon with clear corrindors, rooms and boring traps with thousands of monsters. This dungeons is about secret places, hiden treasures, unusual traps and other cool things. It will be hard to find all secrets and avoid all traps in this dungeon. Some parts of this dungeon are under water. So ofcourse for argonias it will be a bit easier to explore everything.
I can not show you any realy cool things in screenshots or describe them here cause it would be a huge spoiler. I can only say that it\'s realy interesting dungeons with a lot of things you did not see before.


This dungeon is absolutely fully playable right now and it already has a lot of content, but i will update it with new parts, new ways, new secrets...


Just want to tell you again. I can not show you all this cool things i am talking about cause you have to find it yourself. Just download it and explore it. I am sure it will be realy interesting for you.

Recommendations.
You can easily play this mod without anything, but I hightly reomend you using this modes with my (and better use it always) to make exploration even more hard and interesting:
-Tougher traps
Makes traps deal more damage. I could make my traps thougher myself, but i think that if you want it, you will download this mod, and if you do not want traps be so tough you will not download this mod.
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=8344&searchtext=tougher+traps
-Subliminal Traps
Makes pressure plates and tripwires harder to detect. I do not want to say that my traps are soooo easy to detect, but this mod will make some pressure plates less visible. (I\'d do it myself for my dungeon, but I can not).
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2653


Compatibility:
I tried to work as accurate as possible to make this dungeon cause no conflicts. It changes only small parts in the world where i placed entrances.

Changelog:
-23 Sep 2012
Aded new path and some new monsters.
-24 Sep 2012
Sun lights now will turn off in the night.
- 26 Sep 2012
New secret magic room. Cave now a bit darker. Some fixes.
- 4 Nov 2012
New big interesting part.

(Will not write here about small fixes.)


Just to make it absolutely clear: mod is fully on English.

Workshop (with another images):
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=98249260
